        <label for="playlist-select">Add all songs to playlist:</label>
        <select id="playlist-select" name="playlist_id" required>
            <option value="" disabled selected>Select a playlist</option>
            {% for playlist in playlists %}
            <option value="{{ playlist.playlist_id }}">{{ playlist.title }}</option>
            {% endfor %}
        </select>
        <button id="add-album-to-playlist-button" type="submit">Add to Playlist</button>
    </form>

    <p><a href="{{ url_for('albums') }}">Back to Albums</a></p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
```

templates/artists.html
```html
'''
Artist Profiles Page Template
Displays all artists with search and sorting options.
'''
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Artist Profiles</title>
    <style>
        #artists-page { padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
        #artists-grid { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; }
        .artist-card { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 10px; width: 220px; }
        button { margin-top: 5px; padding: 5px 10px; cursor: pointer; }
        #search-artists, #artists-sort { margin: 5px; padding: 5px; font-size: 16px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="artists-page">
    <h1>Artist Profiles</h1>
    <form method="get" action="{{ url_for('artists') }}">
        <input id="search-artists" name="search" type="text" placeholder="Search artists by name" value="{{ search_query }}">
        <select id="artists-sort" name="sort">
            <option value="By Name" {% if sort_option == 'By Name' %}selected{% endif %}>By Name</option>
            <option value="By Genre" {% if sort_option == 'By Genre' %}selected{% endif %}>By Genre</option>
        </select>
        <button type="submit">Search</button>
    </form>
    <div id="artists-grid">
        {% for artist in artists %}
        <div class="artist-card">
            <strong>{{ artist.name }}</strong><br>
            Genre: {{ artist.genre }}<br>
            Country: {{ artist.country }}<br>
            Formation Year: {{ artist.formation_year }}<br>
            <button id="view-artist-button-{{ artist.artist_id }}" onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('artist_profile', artist_id=artist.artist_id) }}'">View Profile</button>
        </div>
        {% else %}
        <p>No artists found.</p>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <p><a href="{{ url_for('dashboard') }}">Back to Dashboard</a></p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
```

